14
00:00:56.080 --> 00:00:57.550
He dove deeply into his art.

15
00:00:57.760 --> 00:01:00.310
He could draw detailed pictures from the memory of a building.

16
00:01:00.311 --> 00:01:03.250
He had only seen once a very rare skill to have,

17
00:01:04.090 --> 00:01:07.060
but when he returned home he had little motivation to do well in school.

18
00:01:07.810 --> 00:01:11.290
After dropping out,
he put all this hope into achieving greatness as an artist.

19
